  Scenario: Manager adds a viewer to a public page, so it is no longer public
    Given user "johno" exists
    Given user "matell" exists
    Given user "crutch" exists
    When I go to the main page
    And I login as "johno"
    And I create "/" page
    And I follow "Manage"
